msgstr ""
"Nastavite samodejne <strong>e-poštne potrditve in opomnike\n"
"</strong> , da bodo stranke obveščene o rezervirani predstavitvi in ​​morebitnih spremembah."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Set up different appointment types (e.g., \"Discovery Call\" and \"Advanced "
"ESG Strategy Demo\") to meet the specific needs of your clients."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite različne vrste sestankov (npr. »Uvodni klic« in »Predstavitev "
"napredne strategije ESG«), da zadostite specifičnim potrebam svojih strank."

