msgstr ""
"Aplikacija <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Časovni "
"list</font></strong> spremlja čas, porabljen za vplivne projekte, in "
"obračunljive ure."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Website "
"App</font></strong> showcases your environmental services and expertise."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Spletna "
"aplikacija</font></strong> predstavlja vaše okoljske storitve in strokovno "
"znanje."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"The Corporate Sustainability Reporting Directive (CSRD) has been adopted "
"into EU law, making sustainability reporting mandatory for certain "
"companies. Stay ahead by preparing your environmental impact reports now. "
"Contact us to ensure your compliance with ease!"
msgstr ""
"Direktiva o poročanju o trajnostnem razvoju podjetij (CSRD) je bila sprejeta"
" v zakonodajo EU, s čimer je poročanje o trajnostnem razvoju za določena "
"podjetja postalo obvezno. Bodite korak pred konkurenco in pripravite svoja "
"poročila o vplivu na okolje že zdaj. Za enostavno zagotovitev skladnosti se "
"obrnite na nas!"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This package is designed to support environmental agencies and consulting "
"firms in optimizing operations, managing projects, and assessing "
"environmental impact with clarity and credibility. Whether conducting carbon"
" footprint analyses, developing sustainability strategies, or guiding "
"organizations in reducing their environmental impact, it enhances overall "
"efficiency and decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Ta paket je zasnovan za podporo okoljskim agencijam in svetovalnim podjetjem "
"pri optimizaciji poslovanja, upravljanju projektov in ocenjevanju vpliva na "
"okolje z jasnostjo in verodostojnostjo. Ne glede na to, ali izvaja analize "
"ogljičnega odtisa, razvija strategije trajnosti ali vodi organizacije pri "
"zmanjševanju njihovega vpliva na okolje, izboljšuje splošno učinkovitost in "
"odločanje."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model:project.task.type,name:environmental_agency.project_task_type_9
msgid "To Do"
msgstr "Opravek"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Track potential clients and manage interactions effectively."
msgstr ""
"Spremljajte potencialne stranke in učinkovito upravljajte interakcije."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model:crm.tag,name:environmental_agency.crm_tag_3
