msgstr "Primer uporabe"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use automated follow-ups and plan activities to stay engaged with prospects "
"and improve conversion rates."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite avtomatizirana nadaljnja obvestila in načrtujte dejavnosti, da "
"ostanete v stiku s potencialnimi strankami in izboljšate stopnje konverzije."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use reporting to analyse time spent on different service categories (e.g., "
"strategy consulting, carbon footprint calculations)."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite poročanje za analizo časa, porabljenega za različne kategorije "
"storitev (npr. strateško svetovanje, izračuni ogljičnega odtisa)."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the<strong> timer functionality </strong>to track time spent on a "
"specific client case."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite<strong>funkcijo časovnika </strong>za sledenje časa, porabljenega "
"za določen primer stranke."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"We actively engage with our community to promote environmental awareness and"
" participate in local green initiatives, fostering a collective effort "
"toward a more sustainable future."
msgstr ""
"Aktivno sodelujemo z našo skupnostjo pri spodbujanju okoljske ozaveščenosti "
"in sodelujemo v lokalnih zelenih pobudah, s čimer spodbujamo skupna "
"prizadevanja za bolj trajnostno prihodnost."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3082
msgid ""
"We are a team of passionate people whose goal is to improve everyone's life "
"through disruptive products. We build great products to solve your business "
"problems. Our products are designed for small to medium size companies "
"willing to optimize their performance."
msgstr ""
"Smo ekipa strastnih ljudi, katerih cilj je izboljšati življenje vseh z "
"revolucionarnimi izdelki. Ustvarjamo odlične izdelke za reševanje vaših "
"poslovnih težav. Naši izdelki so namenjeni malim in srednje velikim "
"podjetjem, ki želijo optimizirati svoje delovanje."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"We develop tailored strategies and solutions to address your unique "
"environmental challenges and goals, promoting sustainability and impact."
msgstr ""
"Razvijamo prilagojene strategije in rešitve za reševanje vaših edinstvenih "
"okoljskih izzivov in ciljev, pri čemer spodbujamo trajnost in vpliv."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"We implement sustainable practices across all aspects of our operations, "
"from reducing waste and conserving resources to supporting eco-friendly "
"initiatives."
msgstr ""
"Trajnostne prakse izvajamo v vseh vidikih našega delovanja, od zmanjševanja "
"odpadkov in varčevanja z viri do podpiranja okolju prijaznih pobud."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"We prioritize energy efficiency in our operations, adopting practices and "
"technologies that reduce energy consumption and lower our carbon footprint."
msgstr ""
"Pri našem poslovanju dajemo prednost energetski učinkovitosti in uvajamo "
"prakse in tehnologije, ki zmanjšujejo porabo energije in naš ogljični odtis."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome to the <strong>Odoo Environmental Agency Package</strong>!"
msgstr ""
"Dobrodošli v <strong>paketu okoljske agencije Odoo \n"
" \n"
"  </strong>!"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With this module, you can manage opportunities, structure sustainability "
"projects, track consultancy hours, and organize key reports. Features like "
"CRM, Project, and Timesheet simplify daily tasks, while Appointment allows "
"clients to book demos with ease."
msgstr ""
"S tem modulom lahko upravljate priložnosti, strukturirate projekte "
"trajnosti, spremljate svetovalne ure in organizirate ključna poročila. "
"Funkcije, kot so CRM, projekti in časovni list, poenostavljajo vsakodnevna "
"opravila, medtem ko funkcija za sestanke strankam omogoča enostavno "
"rezervacijo predstavitev."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "Bi se radi z nami pogovorili o svoji nastavitvi Odoo ali šli še dlje?"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Do vsake nameščene aplikacije v vaši bazi podatkov Odoo lahko dostopate na "
